      "inner_classes": ["_ResponseCreateSequencer", "ModelAudioTracker"],
      "notes": "WebSocket transport to wss://api.openai.com/v1/realtime. Supports call_id (SIP/Calls API) or model query param. Manages response sequencing and audio buffering."
